"Lately in my class, my teammates blame me whenever something goes wrong. Even after coming home from school, I can’t stop replaying everything in my head. I keep thinking about the jokes, comments, and rumors, and it’s becoming difficult to relax or focus on anything else anymore.",TECHNOLOGY,BULLYING,BULLYING,true
